<HR><H2>Editor command change</H2>
<H3>daemon@ATHENA.MIT.EDU (Sat Jan  6 00:25:40 1996
)</H3>
<PRE>
Date: Sat, 6 Jan 1996 05:58:47 +0100
From: silovic@srce.hr (Miroslav Silovic)
To: coldstuff@tombstone.sunrem.com


I replaced :&lt;text&gt; with ,&lt;text&gt; in the editor interface. This way, you
can do both speech and poses in a room while editting (before, a mistaken
pose mingled your text). The replacement is done on the cold.org, and
will be in the new core (unless we replace it again :) )

	Jenner
